          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section D: Family-Run Business -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Image (Left) -->
        <div class="lg:order-1 relative">
          <div class="rounded-xl bg-gray-300 w-full h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <i class="ri-parent-fill text-9xl text-gray-500"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Content (Right) -->
        <div class="lg:order-2">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
            <i class="ri-team-line text-5xl text-[#10B981] mr-4"></i>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">A Family That Cares</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            <p>
              Being family-owned means we bring a personal touch to every job. We don't just clean your spaceâ€”we
              treat it with the same care and respect we would give our own family's home or business.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our family values of honesty, integrity, and excellence are woven into everything we do. From the
              first phone call to the completion of each service, you'll experience the difference that personal
              attention and genuine care make.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Features List -->
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-2xl text-[#10B981] mr-3"></i>
              <span>Family-owned and operated</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-2xl text-[#10B981] mr-3"></i>
              <span>Personal oversight on every job</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-2xl text-[#10B981] mr-3"></i>
              <span>Built on trust and integrity</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-2xl text-[#10B981] mr-3"></i>
              <span>Long-term client relationships</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-2xl text-[#10B981] mr-3"></i>
              <span>Community-focused</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-600">
              <i class="ri-check-line text-2xl text-[#10B981] mr-3"></i>
              <span>Personalized service</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Flare Element #2: Testimonial Banner -->
  <section class="flare-element">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
      <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
        "The best cleaning service we've ever used. Professional, reliable, and they treat our office like it's their own."
      </div>
      <div class="text-white/90 text-lg">
        â€” Sarah Johnson, Office Manager at Tech Solutions Inc.
      </div>
